Class DcMotorEx

java.lang.Object
ftc.crazycatladies.nyan.subsystem.Subsystem
ftc.crazycatladies.nyan.actuators.DcMotorEx
Direct Known Subclasses:
MultiPositionMotor
public class DcMotorEx
extends Subsystem
Subsystem wrapper for DcMotor. Caches data to avoid unnecessary communication with hub. Provides a state machine for running to a specified position

      Description copied from class: Subsystem
      Perform OpMode loop activities. Intended to be called during OpMode.loop or inside a while loop in a LinearOpMode.
